<section class="wp-block-argc-intro-1 container text-center" id="Section0"><div class="container top-bottom-space"><div class="row"><div class="col-sm-12  wow fadeInUp"><h1 class="main-title">Welcome to Dubai Hills Golf Club</h1><div class="max-width"><p class="small-text mtp10">Tee off to a brand-new golfing experience at this serene and lush lifestyle destination located only 15 minutes from Downtown Dubai. Dubai Hills Golf Club is an 18-hole par-72 championship golf course designed by European Golf Design and managed by Troon Golf. Offering a challenge to golfers of all ability, it is a key golfing destination in the region.</p></div></div></div></div></section>



<div class="wp-block-group"><div class="wp-block-group__inner-container is-layout-flow wp-block-group-is-layout-flow"></div></div>



<div class="wp-block-group"><div class="wp-block-group__inner-container is-layout-flow wp-block-group-is-layout-flow">
<section class="wp-block-argc-overlap-section-left content-section overlapping-section"><div class="container"><div class="row align-items-center"><div class="col-sm-7 col-xl-9 wow fadeInLeft" data-wow-duration="1.25s"><div class="lg-img-box"><img decoding="async" src="/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Dubai-Hills-Golf-Club-Sustainability-Pledge.jpg.webp" class="img-fluid img-left-minus mx-auto d-block"/></div></div><div class="col-sm-5 col-xl-3"><div class="content-box  text-left text-sm-left"><i class=""></i><h4 class="">Sustainability Pledge</h4><div class="small-text desc">We have taken our first steps as a club to pledge our commitment to becoming GEO Certified. There are many aspects to becoming a sustainable golf club.</div></div></div></div></div></section>



<section class="wp-block-argc-overlap-section-right content-section overlapping-section overlap img-at-top"><div class="container"><div class="row align-items-center"><div class="col-sm-5 col-xl-3 order-last order-sm-first"><div class="content-box box-top-minus text-left text-sm-left"><i class="th-golf golfpack-045-golfer"></i><h4 class="">Social Membership Offer</h4><div class="small-text desc">Join our Social Membership for 12 months and get your 13th month complimentary. Limited availability, so sign up today by clicking on the link below.</div><a class="btn btn-outline-info border-btn" href="https://www.dubaihillsgolfclub.com/product/social-membership-12-months-offer/" title="JOIN TODAY">JOIN TODAY</a></div></div><div class="col-sm-7 col-xl-9 order-first order-sm-last wow fadeInRight" data-wow-duration="1.25s"><div class="lg-img-box"><img decoding="async" src="https://www.dubaihillsgolfclub.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/SM.jpg.webp" class="img-fluid mx-auto d-block img-right-minus center"/></div></div></div></div></section>



<section class="wp-block-argc-overlap-section-left content-section overlapping-section overlap img-at-top"><div class="container"><div class="row align-items-center"><div class="col-sm-7 col-xl-9 wow fadeInLeft" data-wow-duration="1.25s"><div class="lg-img-box"><img decoding="async" src="https://www.dubaihillsgolfclub.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/TA.jpg.webp" class="img-fluid img-left-minus mx-auto d-block"/></div></div><div class="col-sm-5 col-xl-3"><div class="content-box  text-left text-sm-left"><i class=""></i><h4 class="">Gift Vouchers</h4><div class="small-text desc">Are you looking for that perfect Gift? Why not give your loved one a gift voucher for a round of golf or if they want to sharpen up their game, then a golf lesson. </div><a class="btn btn-outline-info border-btn" href="https://www.dubaihillsgolfclub.com/product/gift-vouchers/" title="BUY NOW">BUY NOW</a></div></div></div></div></section>



<div class="wp-block-columns container content-section is-layout-flex wp-container-core-columns-is-layout-1 wp-block-columns-is-layout-flex">
<div class="wp-block-column is-vertically-aligned-center is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow" style="flex-basis:45%">
<h2 class="wp-block-heading main-title main-title-border-left text-left mbp35">SPONSORSHIP OPPORTUNITIES</h2>



<div class="wp-block-group content-box text-left text-sm-left"><div class="wp-block-group__inner-container is-layout-flow wp-block-group-is-layout-flow">
<h5 class="wp-block-heading text-capitalize"></h5>



<p class="small-text">Golf club sponsorship can be a powerful marketing strategy, allowing brands to reach a highly engaged audience of affluent, active consumers. By aligning with the prestige and lifestyle of the sport, sponsors can build brand awareness, drive product sales, and create lasting connections with loyal golf enthusiasts.</p>
</div></div>



<div class="wp-block-group content-box text-left text-sm-left"><div class="wp-block-group__inner-container is-layout-flow wp-block-group-is-layout-flow">
<h5 class="wp-block-heading text-capitalize">Audience Reach</h5>



<p class="small-text">Golf club sponsorships provide access to a high-income, loyal fan base that values quality and exclusivity.</p>
</div></div>



<div class="wp-block-group content-box text-left text-sm-left"><div class="wp-block-group__inner-container is-layout-flow wp-block-group-is-layout-flow">
<h5 class="wp-block-heading text-capitalize">Brand Visibility</h5>



<p class="small-text">Prominent placement of logos and signage at the golf course ensures constant exposure for the sponsor&#8217;s brand.</p>
</div></div>



<div class="wp-block-group content-box text-left text-sm-left"><div class="wp-block-group__inner-container is-layout-flow wp-block-group-is-layout-flow">
<h5 class="wp-block-heading text-capitalize">Hospitality Opportunities</h5>



<p class="small-text">Sponsors can host client events, pro-am tournaments, and other VIP experiences to build relationships and foster brand loyalty.</p>
</div></div>



<div class="wp-block-buttons is-layout-flex wp-block-buttons-is-layout-flex"></div>



<p class="btn-custom-primary mtp35"><a href="https://form.typeform.com/to/iDLQ4GUL" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">Learn More</a></p>
</div>



<div class="wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow" style="flex-basis:55%">
<figure class="wp-block-image size-full wow fadeInRight img-fluid w-full"><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" width="754" height="754" src="https://www.dubaihillsgolfclub.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/DSC05062-copy.jpg" alt="" class="wp-image-120814" srcset="https://www.dubaihillsgolfclub.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/DSC05062-copy.jpg 754w, https://www.dubaihillsgolfclub.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/DSC05062-copy-400x400.jpg 400w, https://www.dubaihillsgolfclub.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/DSC05062-copy-150x150.jpg 150w, https://www.dubaihillsgolfclub.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/DSC05062-copy-100x100.jpg 100w, https://www.dubaihillsgolfclub.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/DSC05062-copy-450x450.jpg 450w, https://www.dubaihillsgolfclub.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/DSC05062-copy-600x600.jpg 600w" sizes="(max-width: 754px) 100vw, 754px" /></figure>
</div>
</div>



<section class="wp-block-argc-overlap-section-right content-section overlapping-section"><div class="container"><div class="row align-items-center"><div class="col-sm-5 col-xl-3 order-last order-sm-first"><div class="content-box box-top-minus text-left text-sm-left"><i class="th-golf golfpack-045-golfer"></i><h4 class="">Golf</h4><div class="small-text desc">Set against the striking Dubai skyline with an iconic backdrop of the Burj Khalifa, visible on many holes, it leaves golfers wanting to come back for more.</div><a class="btn btn-outline-info border-btn" href="/golf/" title="SEE MORE">SEE MORE</a></div></div><div class="col-sm-7 col-xl-9 order-first order-sm-last wow fadeInRight" data-wow-duration="1.25s"><div class="lg-img-box"><img decoding="async" src="wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Dubai-Hills-Golf-Club-Homepage-golf-inner.jpg" class="img-fluid mx-auto d-block img-right-minus center"/></div></div></div></div></section>



<section class="wp-block-argc-overlap-section-left content-section overlapping-section overlap img-at-top"><div class="container"><div class="row align-items-center"><div class="col-sm-7 col-xl-9 wow fadeInLeft" data-wow-duration="1.25s"><div class="lg-img-box"><img decoding="async" src="wp-content/uploads/2022/08/DHGC-Form-9.jpg" class="img-fluid img-left-minus mx-auto d-block"/></div></div><div class="col-sm-5 col-xl-3"><div class="content-box  text-left text-sm-left"><i class=""></i><h4 class="">Membership Enquiry Form</h4><div class="small-text desc">For more information about our membership packages, click on the button below and fill out the form. Our Membership Manager will then be in touch with all the details.</div><a class="btn btn-outline-info border-btn" href="https://form.typeform.com/to/V3w3yQsu" target="_blank" title="SEE MORE" rel="noopener">SEE MORE</a></div></div></div></div></section>



<section class="wp-block-argc-overlap-section-right content-section overlapping-section overlap img-at-top"><div class="container"><div class="row align-items-center"><div class="col-sm-5 col-xl-3 order-last order-sm-first"><div class="content-box box-top-minus text-left text-sm-left"><i class="th-golf golfpack-045-golfer"></i><h4 class="">Academy<br/> by Troon</h4><div class="small-text desc">Whether you are a beginner taking your first swings or putts in golf or a seasoned amateur we have lessons that will help you shoot your best scores ever.</div><a class="btn btn-outline-info border-btn" href="/academy/" title="SEE MORE">SEE MORE</a></div></div><div class="col-sm-7 col-xl-9 order-first order-sm-last wow fadeInRight" data-wow-duration="1.25s"><div class="lg-img-box"><img decoding="async" src="/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Junior-May-2023.jpg.webp" class="img-fluid mx-auto d-block img-right-minus center"/></div></div></div></div></section>
</div></div>



<div class="wp-block-group"><div class="wp-block-group__inner-container is-layout-flow wp-block-group-is-layout-flow"></div></div>



<section class="wp-block-argc-bg-img-with-box member-bg clearfix home-membership" style="background: url(/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Dubai-Hills-Golf-Club-Homepage-Membership1.jpg) no-repeat center top; background-size: cover"><div class="container clearfix top-bottom-space"><div class="row align-items-center"><div class="col-sm-12"><div class="card text-center float-sm-right shadow-lg card-style wow fadeInRight" data-wow-duration="1.25s"><div class="card-body"><h5 class="card-title">Golf Membership</h5><div class="card-text">Become a member of our iconic golf course and take advantage of all the benefits including access to Montgomerie Golf Club Dubai and Arabian Ranches Golf Club.</div><a class="card-link" href="/membership/" title="LEARN MORE">LEARN MORE<i class="fal fa-arrow-right"></i></a></div></div></div></div></div></section>



